<h1>About Delivery</h1>
<h4>What comes with each delivery?</h4>
<p>Every box contains enough ingredients to make 8 full servings of juice.  We pre-portion the ingredients for you to save you time and also minimize wasted food.  No more watching ‘extra’ produce slowly spoil in your refrigerator! </p>
<h4>Do I need to pay extra for shipping?</h4>
<p>Nope!  The price you see on the website is the full price inclusive of shipping.  We want to make the experience as easy as possible, and therefore we don’t surprise you with extra shipping fees.</p>
<h4>Can I change delivery to a different day of the week?</h4>
<p>At the moment we are doing all of our shipments on the same day, but we plan to offer multiple delivery dates over time.  Please tell us what works best for you so that we can fine-tune the delivery options!</p>
<h4>Where do you deliver?</h4>
<p>For now we deliver to zip codes that are within 1-day shipping of New York City. If we do not yet deliver to your zip code, fear not!  We expect to ship to more locations soon and will send you an email when we reach your area.</p>

