<h1>About Farmivore</h1>
<h4>So, what's the deal with Farmivore?</h4>
<p>Like many people, we are concerned about the growth and persistence of unhealthy eating habits in our country.  Eating a well-balanced diet can be very challenging.  We wanted to create a subscription service that would encourage people to maintain regular consumption of vegetables and fruit in order to lead a healthier lifestyle.  Juicing is an excellent way to boost nutritional intake, plus it’s fun and makes you feel good!
</p>
